com.googlecode.transmuter.converter
Annotation Type Converts

@Documented
@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Converts

Intended to mark a method as a prospective converter method.

Not all methods can be converter methods. This annotation should be used only on methods which can be successfully provided.

Author:
Humberto S. N. dos Anjos
See Also:
Converts.EagerProvider, Converts.LazyProvider
